  <brief_title>Invasive Aspergillosis After Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation (HSCT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Incidence of Invasive Aspergillosis in Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation Patients: an Italian Prospective Multicentre Study</official_title>
