  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of incidence of invasive aspergillosis in patients who have undergone an
      allogeneic stem cell transplantation, with particular regard to the role of galactomannan
      assay and of early TC scan in asymptomatic patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
